{"tid":663522,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"各位大佬入一入嚟","createTime":"2018-05-13T11:09:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-13T15:10:01.000Z","uid":60398,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8504da104c70684c3d5895d289c899745c1253d6","tid":663522,"uid":60398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T11:09:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">近幾年多咗好多同扶手電梯嘅意外</span></span><br />\n<br />\n升降機失控　狂飆40秒撼𨋢槽頂<br />\n夫婦爆頭傷頸椎命危<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180409/20356175\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180409%2F20356175&d=l56OeejL4wiwyf4oeJug0ozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=a5d4cef8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180409%2F20356175&h=03ee79ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180409/20356175</a><br />\n<br />\n升降機殺人真相曝光　事主遭𨋢門夾腳扯至上層墮槽<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180511/mobile/bkn-20180511161520640-0511_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180511%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180511161520640-0511_00822_001.html&d=l56OeejL4wiwyf4oeJug0ozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=ca3e9342\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180511/mobile/bkn-20180511161520640-0511_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n【電梯急升】評分漏洞、趕工惹禍、低價搶標　電梯行業良莠不齊<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/176805/%E9%9B%BB%E6%A2%AF%E6%80%A5%E5%8D%87-%E8%A9%95%E5%88%86%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E-%E8%B6%95%E5%B7%A5%E6%83%B9%E7%A6%8D-%E4%BD%8E%E5%83%B9%E6%90%B6%E6%A8%99-%E9%9B%BB%E6%A2%AF%E8%A1%8C%E6%A5%AD%E8%89%AF%E8%8E%A0%E4%B8%8D%E9%BD%8A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F176805%2F%25E9%259B%25BB%25E6%25A2%25AF%25E6%2580%25A5%25E5%258D%2587-%25E8%25A9%2595%25E5%2588%2586%25E6%25BC%258F%25E6%25B4%259E-%25E8%25B6%2595%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E6%2583%25B9%25E7%25A6%258D-%25E4%25BD%258E%25E5%2583%25B9%25E6%2590%25B6%25E6%25A8%2599-%25E9%259B%25BB%25E6%25A2%25AF%25E8%25A1%258C%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E8%2589%25AF%25E8%258E%25A0%25E4%25B8%258D%25E9%25BD%258A&d=l56OeejL4wiwyf4oeJug0ozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=62fab077\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/176805/%E9%9B%BB%E6%A2%AF%E6%80%A5%E5%8D%87-%E8%A9%95%E5%88%86%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E-%E8%B6%95%E5%B7%A5%E6%83%B9%E7%A6%8D-%E4%BD%8E%E5%83%B9%E6%90%B6%E6%A8%99-%E9%9B%BB%E6%A2%AF%E8%A1%8C%E6%A5%AD%E8%89%AF%E8%8E%A0%E4%B8%8D%E9%BD%8A</a><br />\n<br />\n故障升降機離奇急降　維修師傅遭鍘身命危<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171115/mobile/bkn-20171115103816148-1115_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171115%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20171115103816148-1115_00822_001.html&d=l56OeejL4wiwyf4oeJug0ozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=64cc276e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171115/mobile/bkn-20171115103816148-1115_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n何文田站炒扶手梯　男乘客行慢兩秒就<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180108/mobile/bkn-20180108153753204-0108_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180108%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180108153753204-0108_00822_001.html&d=l56OeejL4wiwyf4oeJug0ozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=d1d43992\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180108/mobile/bkn-20180108153753204-0108_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n西鐵屯門站炒扶手梯 嚇到市民雞飛狗走<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180406/58038993\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180406%2F58038993&d=l56OeejL4wiwyf4oeJug0ozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=e914b9a1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180406%2F58038993&h=4235c335\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180406/58038993</a><br />\n<br />\n朗豪坊扶手電梯意外18傷<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/1732648/2017%E7%84%A6%E9%BB%9E%E5%A4%A7%E4%BA%8B%E5%9B%9E%E9%A1%A7%EF%B9%95%E6%9C%97%E8%B1%AA%E5%9D%8A%E6%89%B6%E6%89%8B%E9%9B%BB%E6%A2%AF%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%9618%E5%82%B7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F1732648%2F2017%25E7%2584%25A6%25E9%25BB%259E%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25BA%258B%25E5%259B%259E%25E9%25A1%25A7%25EF%25B9%2595%25E6%259C%2597%25E8%25B1%25AA%25E5%259D%258A%25E6%2589%25B6%25E6%2589%258B%25E9%259B%25BB%25E6%25A2%25AF%25E6%2584%258F%25E5%25A4%259618%25E5%2582%25B7&d=l56OeejL4wiwyf4oeJug0ozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=b07d9dbf\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/1732648/2017%E7%84%A6%E9%BB%9E%E5%A4%A7%E4%BA%8B%E5%9B%9E%E9%A1%A7%EF%B9%95%E6%9C%97%E8%B1%AA%E5%9D%8A%E6%89%B6%E6%89%8B%E9%9B%BB%E6%A2%AF%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%9618%E5%82%B7</a><br />\n<br />\n【恐怖意外】安蔭邨升降機突上升　維修工被夾雙腳凌空　送院不治<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/162643/%E6%81%90%E6%80%96%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%96-%E5%AE%89%E8%94%AD%E9%82%A8%E5%8D%87%E9%99%8D%E6%A9%9F%E7%AA%81%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%87-%E7%B6%AD%E4%BF%AE%E5%B7%A5%E8%A2%AB%E5%A4%BE%E9%9B%99%E8%85%B3%E5%87%8C%E7%A9%BA-%E9%80%81%E9%99%A2%E4%B8%8D%E6%B2%BB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F162643%2F%25E6%2581%2590%25E6%2580%2596%25E6%2584%258F%25E5%25A4%2596-%25E5%25AE%2589%25E8%2594%25AD%25E9%2582%25A8%25E5%258D%2587%25E9%2599%258D%25E6%25A9%259F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%258D%2587-%25E7%25B6%25AD%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%25A4%25BE%25E9%259B%2599%25E8%2585%25B3%25E5%2587%258C%25E7%25A9%25BA-%25E9%2580%2581%25E9%2599%25A2%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25B2%25BB&d=l56OeejL4wiwyf4oeJug0ozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=608cbf8f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/162643/%E6%81%90%E6%80%96%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%96-%E5%AE%89%E8%94%AD%E9%82%A8%E5%8D%87%E9%99%8D%E6%A9%9F%E7%AA%81%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%87-%E7%B6%AD%E4%BF%AE%E5%B7%A5%E8%A2%AB%E5%A4%BE%E9%9B%99%E8%85%B3%E5%87%8C%E7%A9%BA-%E9%80%81%E9%99%A2%E4%B8%8D%E6%B2%BB</a><br />\n<br />\n小弟有屋企人都係做呢行<br />\n我由細到大都成日會聽到佢講整嘅嘢<br />\n有時佢仲會俾啲鄰國扶手電梯/夾死人嘅片我睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">[！慎入！]</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/xT5sFh8ltIE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FxT5sFh8ltIE&d=l56OeejL4wiwyf4oeJug0ozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=6738302e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/xT5sFh8ltIE</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/66fUCVj2VWY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F66fUCVj2VWY&d=l56OeejL4wiwyf4oeJug0ozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=50a64b83\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/66fUCVj2VWY</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2015年大陸「食人電梯」慘劇<br />\n<a href=\"http://evchk.wikia.com/wiki/2015%E5%B9%B4%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B8%E3%80%8C%E9%A3%9F%E4%BA%BA%E9%9B%BB%E6%A2%AF%E3%80%8D%E6%85%98%E5%8A%87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fevchk.wikia.com%2Fwiki%2F2015%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2599%25B8%25E3%2580%258C%25E9%25A3%259F%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%259B%25BB%25E6%25A2%25AF%25E3%2580%258D%25E6%2585%2598%25E5%258A%2587&d=l56OeejL4wiwyf4oeJug0ozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=abc42715\" target=\"_blank\">http://evchk.wikia.com/wiki/2015%E5%B9%B4%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B8%E3%80%8C%E9%A3%9F%E4%BA%BA%E9%9B%BB%E6%A2%AF%E3%80%8D%E6%85%98%E5%8A%87</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/WmjQCd9f90U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FWmjQCd9f90U&d=l56OeejL4wiwyf4oeJug0ozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=b2c71e6a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/WmjQCd9f90U</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一路以嚟我都係俾佢嚇到疴青屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係我當時會諗 香港點都無支那咁離譜 咁多事故嘅<br />\n而我果位屋企人喺十年前有講過 呢行人工低 無乜後生入行 好辛苦 第時啲啊 扶手梯會成日出事<br />\n<br />\n啊~屌佢個老尾 依加就真係嚟料啦<br />\n同身邊嘅朋友講 佢地就話<br />\n「咁驚你唔好出街啊笨！」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大佬啊 香港人真係未發生喺自己身上都唔知驚<br />\n<br />\n我有問過我屋企人 點解唔搞下罷工 人地因航都成功增取到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  佢就話曬氣 廿幾年前搞過 之後班人炒曬<br />\n個工會又廢 依加人工低 又多嘢做<br />\n佢話有好多師傅接到order 去到就是鳩但停咗㗎就話當維修緊 事實上就喺入面㩒電話 同埋訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n電梯維修員罷工爭加薪 <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20081004/11681191\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20081004%2F11681191&d=l56OeejL4wiwyf4oeJug0ozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=4b6a29ae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20081004%2F11681191&h=ddc3119b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20081004/11681191</a><br />\n咁廿幾年前新聞我就揾唔到 而呢單都無講過有無炒曬啲師傅<br />\n<br />\n老實講 整師傅係好撚辛苦 你地唔好話毅進仔讀得少書 抵佢咁少人工<br />\n屌你老尾你睇下班猶差？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢班撚樣強姦市民 做嘢斷鳩估 佢地又值28000？<br />\n但係整師傅係保障到市民嘅安全 大佬無佢地唔知幾多會出事啦 一日分分鐘有一單夾死人 呢行咁撚低人工/福利又閪 邊個有心同你做啊？<br />\n<br />\n我想講 撘/扶手電梯係無得避 你唔好諗住下下都行樓梯 呢樣根本無乜可能 而且香港人多 扶手電梯一發生事故就好大劑<br />\n如果你地依加唔去爭取 呢個行業只會慢慢收皮<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">到時出事有可能係你 亦都有可能係你嘅屋企人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n最後 香港人要團結！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75bf344ba674defa96d332edc90d67ec594d2dd5","tid":663522,"uid":60398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T11:10:40.000Z","msg":"炒梯點避啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果好似又一城咁<br />\n唔通你跳落街啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n避唔到就會變人肉攪拌機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嘩屌你老尾真係好撚恐怖"},{"pid":"d908a96585a8a5502ce8bc44aa48e25557481bae","tid":663522,"uid":60398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T11:11:51.000Z","msg":"想多啲人關注升降機/扶手電梯嘅安全問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e8490e89f990b717e9d9d044e25c7e08d9f6376","tid":663522,"uid":60398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T11:13:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fb1ba610d38ebb5886be9865471b1ec387478b7","tid":663522,"uid":60398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T11:14:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e824dbf8fc531cf4d25e0f6adf2560421976068f","tid":663522,"uid":60398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201