e":"2018-05-13T11:31:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有啲顧問會指定啲大公司做lift <br />\n例如其士 otis 特別係新起既樓<br />\n但而加好少人入行<br />\nhd grad起薪萬八都冇入肯入<br />\n遲早出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個個都咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e6121c62f5d27433c84a5df4b412cb8ada878b3","tid":663522,"uid":60398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T11:37:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10b7660d106991e9cf985bf1e9812140d3e9b20f","tid":663522,"uid":60398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T11:47:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e8a37ab304fcaf57e8cab0a05cb6c82b91d4e83","tid":663522,"uid":90802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6585051d1fea481063790761104460c1ecedfeaf","tid":663522,"uid":60398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T11:31:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有啲顧問會指定啲大公司做lift <br />\n例如其士 otis 特別係新起既樓<br />\n但而加好少人入行<br />\nhd grad起薪萬八都冇入肯入<br />\n遲早出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個個都咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T15:10:01.000Z","msg":"重點係堅好少人入行 有個frd 萬8蚊起薪 仲入職送電話同其他福利都唔要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}